performance.title: Performance Hubi
performance.info-polycount: Waxaan ku talineynaa in aad goobta isticmaalaan wax ka badan 50,000 saddexagal for qalabka mobile.
performance.info-material: Waxaan ku talinaynaa in la isticmaalayo ma ka badan 25 qalabka u gaar ah ee goobtaada si loo yareeyo wicitaanada barbaro on qalabka mobile.
performance.info-texture: Waxaan kugula talineynaa qaabab aad isticmaasho wax ka badan 256MB of video RAM for qalabka mobile. Waxaan sidoo kale ku talineynaa inaan la isticmaalin qaabab ka weyn 2048 x 2048.
performance.info-lights: Inkastoo nalalka firfircoon aan awood on qalabka mobile, waxaan ku talinaynaa in la isticmaalayo ma badnayn 3 nalalka in aad goobta (marka laga reebo daarmayaay'e nalalka daarmayaay'e) si aad goobta in ay ordi on ku-takhasusay dhamaadka hoose.
performance.info-fileSize: Waxaan kugula talineynaa in size file kama dambaysta ah oo aan ka badnayn 16MB xiriir bandwidth hooseeyo. Yaraynta size file yarayn doonaa waqtiga ay qaadataa si aad u soo dejisan goobta.
